    faq_a: `Powder-coated aluminum blinds are the most cost-effective durable window treatment for Solana Beach investment and rental properties — the metal construction is inherently salt-air resistant with no warping or corrosion risk, and individual slats can be replaced without removing the entire blind. iL Progetto supplies commercial-gauge aluminum blinds in anodized finish options appropriate for a coastal environment and carries cordless configurations suited to rental properties. For the Cedros-adjacent homeowner who wants something more design-expressive, we offer these as a practical base-level option for secondary spaces.`,
