    faq_a: `Room-darkening fabric-vane vertical blinds provide the most immediate daytime privacy for sliding glass doors on Solana Beach's tight lots where a neighboring deck may be within 10–15 feet of your own. iL Progetto installs fabric vanes in privacy-opaque room-darkening weights that block sightlines from adjacent outdoor spaces while still allowing the door to operate freely and the vanes to be fully retracted when privacy isn't needed. UV-rated anodized aluminum track hardware handles the coastal salt-air environment without the corrosion and binding that standard tracks develop.`,
