    faq_a: `Panel-track blinds in trade-quality woven and textured fabrics are the most architecturally intentional solution for wide window walls in Solana Beach's design-aware homes. Unlike vertical louvre systems, wide fabric panels in sheer or solar-weave constructions read as designed elements — something a Cedros Design District-adjacent homeowner would choose intentionally. iL Progetto selects panel fabrics in the neutral, textured palettes that design-conscious Solana Beach interiors favor and calibrates panel widths so the stack position doesn't compromise the narrow-lot window's view potential.`,
