    faq_a: `Woven wood shades in their natural open-weave form are not a strong privacy product — the open construction allows sightlines at closer distances. For Solana Beach's narrow-lot context, iL Progetto adds a privacy liner during fabrication that blocks interior views from neighboring windows while preserving the organic woven texture that makes these shades appealing. The result is the natural material aesthetic that Solana Beach's design-conscious clientele wants combined with the genuine daytime privacy the lot geometry demands. Blackout lining available for bedrooms.`,
