    faq_a: `Standard sheer shades provide one-way privacy at normal distances — you can see out, neighbors at a typical distance cannot see in clearly. On Solana Beach's narrowest lots in Solana Hills and Fletcher Cove, where a neighbor's window may be only 15–20 feet away, iL Progetto recommends sheer shades in the denser 1% openness vane fabrics that provide stronger one-way privacy effect at close range. Motorized models allow angle adjustment to manage specific problem sightlines from particular neighboring windows.`,
