    faq_a: `Sheer drapes in performance solar-weave constructions provide meaningful daytime privacy at normal viewing distances while maintaining the luminous coastal light quality that Solana Beach homeowners value. For the closest-proximity situations in Solana Hills and Fletcher Cove, iL Progetto layers sheer drapes over a solar roller shade — the roller provides privacy reinforcement when needed, and the sheer panels create the soft visual warmth for all other hours. Performance sheer fabrics resist the UV yellowing that the Solana Beach coastal exposure would cause on standard polyester sheers.`,
