    faq_a: `Solana Beach's afternoon onshore breeze is real but manageable with the right awning specification. iL Progetto installs retractable lateral-arm awnings with wind-sensor motor controls that automatically retract when gusts exceed the safe operational threshold — protecting the fabric investment and eliminating the need for the homeowner to monitor conditions manually. Cassette-enclosed models fully protect the fabric from morning marine-layer moisture when retracted. Solution-dyed acrylic canvas resists both the salt-air bleaching and the UV fading that the Solana Beach coastal environment would cause on lesser materials.`,
