    faq_a: `For RSF guest houses, casitas, and secondary bedrooms where the primary design investment is elsewhere, premium faux-wood blinds are a quality-appropriate solution that holds up under RSF's warm inland summer temperatures without the thermal expansion risk that real wood faces in this climate. iL Progetto carries faux-wood in the warmest stain tones — rich walnuts, warm espressos — that coordinate with the Spanish Colonial and Mediterranean interiors typical of RSF guest structures. Cordless lifts and motorized options available. Custom-cut to exact window dimensions.`,
