    faq_a: `Agricultural and utility buildings on RSF properties — horse barns, equipment storage, workshop spaces — need window treatments that are completely impervious to the temperature extremes, dust, and hay debris that interior environments like these generate. Commercial-gauge powder-coated aluminum blinds from iL Progetto are the correct specification: no wood to warp in RSF's summer heat, no fabric to absorb dust or allergens, and individual slat replacement when needed without removing the entire blind. Slat widths up to 2 inches for broad coverage on ranch-scale window openings.`,
