    faq_a: `Estate-grade sheer shades — wider vanes, heavier sheer face fabric, precision-fit motorized headrails — are an appropriate choice for RSF formal living rooms where the goal is diffused natural light rather than view preservation. iL Progetto specifies the top-tier sheer shade product lines for Covenant installations, fabricated to the large window dimensions characteristic of RSF estate great rooms. For the afternoon sun exposure common in RSF's warmer inland climate, the vane angle adjusts to protect antique furnishings and artwork from the UV load without eliminating the natural light quality.`,
